s|TAG_MOVIE_NEWS|<A ALT="" TITLE="Bollywood Movie News" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2006/12_04_2006.html">12/07/2006</A> <br> Eros International has set the date of 23rd February, 2007 for the release of <A ALT="" TITLE="Provoked Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2006/provoked.html">Provoked</A> starring <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai</A> , Naveen Andrews and Nandita Das, with music by <A ALT="" TITLE="AR Rahman" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/music_director/ar_rahman/bollywood_ar_rahman_filmography.html">AR Rahman</A> .<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><A ALT="" TITLE="Bollywood Movie News" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2006/12_04_2006.html">12/07/2006</A> <br> Eros International has set the date of 23rd February, 2007 for the release of <A ALT="" TITLE="Provoked Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2006/provoked.html">Provoked</A> starring <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai</A> , Naveen Andrews and Nandita Das, with music by <A ALT="" TITLE="AR Rahman" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/music_director/ar_rahman/bollywood_ar_rahman_filmography.html">AR Rahman</A> .<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>Eros To Distribute 'Provoked' Starring Aishwarya Rai</b> <br> <font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Bollywood Movie News" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2006/08_21_2006.html">08/24/2006</A> </font> <br> Eros International has acquired the rights to distribute <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai</A> ’s latest release, Provoked, in the UK, the US and India. <A ALT="" TITLE="Provoked Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2006/provoked.html">Provoked</A> is directed by Jag Mundhra and casts Rai (Bride and Prejudice, Devdas, Hum Dil De Chuke Sanam) in the lead role, with Miranda Richardson, Robbie Coltrane and Nandita Das. The movie is based on true story of a Punjabi woman named Kiranjit Ahluwalia who moves to England and marries a man who subjects her to violent physical abuse.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>Aishwarya Rai At Cannes film festival confirmed that she was the victim of domestic violence</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Bollywood Movie News" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2006/05_15_2006.html">05/24/2006</A> <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai</A> is currently at the Cannes film festival to promote her film <A ALT="" TITLE="Provoked Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2006/provoked.html">Provoked</A> . This is were the sensuous Indian former Miss World confirmed that she was a victim of domestic violence which by considence is the subjet of her next movie, <A ALT="" TITLE="Provoked Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2006/provoked.html">Provoked</A> , directed by Jagmohan Mundhra. It is a known fact that Salman and Ash shared a strange relationship, and that Salman was extremely possessive of his then lady love Ash. The film is expected to be released September 2006. <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai</A> also made a reference to a future biography on herself that she will write.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>Aishwarya Rai's Provoked to be screened at Cannes</b> <br> Date: 02/07/2006 <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai</A> will make another appearance at the Cannes film festival in May, this time for her role of a woman struggling for dignity in the film <A ALT="" TITLE="Provoked Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2006/provoked.html">Provoked</A> . The film is directed by Jag Mundhra and stars <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai</A> and Naveen Andrews. Ash has also being a jury member at the Cannes and four years ago her film <A ALT="" TITLE="Devdas Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2002/devdas.html">Devdas</A> was screened at the Cannes. The film is produced by Dr. J Murli Manohar, who will have another film, Infinite Justice, also screened at Cannes. <A ALT="" TITLE="Provoked Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2006/provoked.html">Provoked</A> is being distributed by an American company – Lee Daniel's Entertainment which also distributed a <A ALT="" TITLE="Halle Berry" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/hollywood/actress/halle_berry/hollywood_halle_berry.html">Halle Berry</A> starrer, Monster's Ball.<br><hr size="1" width="100%">|g
